No. —, original.

New Jersey v. State of New York et al. Motion submitted May 13, 1929. Decided May 20, 1929. Messrs. Duane E. Minard and Williams A. Stevens for complainant. Messrs. Hamilton Ward, Attorney General of New York, . and Albert J. Danaher for the State of New York. Per Curiam:

Motion for leave to file a bill of complaint herein is granted, and process is ordered to issue, returnable on Monday, May 27 next.
